Package: classic
Version: 2.4.1-1
Type: theme
Name: Theme Classic
Description: Optional Theme. Traditional.
 Works execent in all browsers.
 Fine in IOS. (one touch -> hover), (two touch -> click).
 Ok in Android Tablets, smartphones.. (The click event has been converted to a Dashboard menu).
 This theme was first thought to be a replacement for the Default theme, but many testers wanted to
 keep the Default theme. So will just wait and see.
